videos.description: Gabe DeVoe hits a jumper off the glass to end the Tigers' five-minute scoreless drought.
videos.headline: DeVoe ends Clemson's drought on bank shot

videos.description: Marcquise Reed comes up with the steal and finishes on the other end with a big slam.
videos.headline: Clemson's Reed throws down off steal

videos.description: A Clemson basketball fan celebrates with the mascot after hitting a full-court putt to win $10,000.
videos.headline: Clemson fan sinks $10,000 putt

videos.description: Deng Adel throws down a fast-break dunk that ties the game at 53 late in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Louisville's Adel ties game with slam) 2018/01/06

videos.description: Marcquise Reed hits an acrobatic layup to puts Clemson up four over Louisville in overtime.
